'''Anezwu asbegsan''' (Yettusma ar [[Asebges|usebges]]) d [[anezwu]] i d-yezgan deg tlemmast n [[tagnit|tegnit]] gar n sin [[ijeṛdan n tehri]] 10° n [[agafa|ugafa]] d [[aneẓẓul|uneẓẓul]] n [[tiṭṭ n tfukt]], yettwasen s weẓɣal d walluy n tseddaṛin ɣef teɣzi n useggas, d tuget n [[ageffur|ugeffur]] ayen yettaǧǧan  [[Tiẓgi tasbegsant|tiẓegwa tisbegsatin]] ad ugtent deg yideggan-nni, [[Tiẓgi n Amaẓun]] d tin yettwassnen yakk gar-asent.

== Ideggan n unezwu-a ==
Yettili deg ugafa n [[Tamrikt n Wenẓul]], timura n [[Aneẓul n usamar n Asya]], [[Sudan]], [[Tafriqt talemmast]] d [[Ɣinya tamaynut]]

